With this, you can do every thing about Weibo on terminal.

##Config File##
Location:~/.weibo

Options:
* username  
* password
* author_color
  The highlight color of author's name.  
  colors: HEADER/BLUE/GREEN/WARNING/FAIL/END  
* app_id
  The app id got from Sina, you can regist another app on open.weibo.com, or just use mine.  
  Please do not do anything bad with it :)
* width
  Max width of the output
